										<p>網站使用條款</p>
									</div>

									<h2 class="accordion-header">3. 隱私權政策</h2>
									<div class="accordion-content third-row">
										<p>隱私權政策</p>
									</div>

									<h2 class="accordion-header">4. 免責聲明</h2>
